These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: snooker, canasta, monopoly, poker, mah-jongg, scrabble, bridge
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, photographer, accountant, chef, nurse, social-worker, paramedic
House: victorian, cape-cod, palace, farmhouse, craftsman, tower, cottage
City: prague, miami, liverpool, rome, venice, new-york, boston
 1. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
 2. the craftsman house is the chef##1
 3. the person traveling to venice is the palace house##1
 4. the photographer is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the fisherman is on the right of the paramedic##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the palace house##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the nurse##1
 8. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to boston and the social-worker##2
 9. the nurse is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
10. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
11. the victorian house is the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the person playing mah-jongg is the person traveling to prague##1
13. the person playing snooker is on the left of the accountant##1
14. the social-worker is the person traveling to liverpool##1
15. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the paramedic##1
16. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
17. the tower house is on the left of the accountant##1
18. the person playing bridge is on the right of the nurse##1
19. the cottage house is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Game      | canasta  | scrabble        | mah-jongg | monopoly      | poker     | snooker      | bridge     |
| Job   | photographer | chef         | paramedic   | fisherman | social-worker    | nurse | accountant |
| House         | palace | craftsman | victorian | cape-cod | cottage  | tower  | farmhouse    |
| City     | venice  | new-york         | prague     | miami    | liverpool | rome     | boston     |

